{"id":802,"date":"2020-01-27T19:48:04","date_gmt":"2020-01-27T19:48:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.uplaysports.co.uk\/?page_id=802"},"modified":"2020-01-27T19:48:07","modified_gmt":"2020-01-27T19:48:07","slug":"faq","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.uplaysports.co.uk\/faq\/","title":{"rendered":"Frequently Asked Questions"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[et_pb_section fb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243;][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243;]<\/p>\n<h3>Frequently Asked Questions<\/h3>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_accordion _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243;][et_pb_accordion_item open=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; custom_css_main_element=&#8221;display: none;&#8221;][\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Who are we?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p><span class=\"s1\">Here at uPlayMultiSports we deliver high quality multi-sport coaching programmes for children. Our ethos is about participation, staying active and having fun! We want everyone who comes to our camps to enjoy experiencing as wide a range of activities as possible in a safe and friendly environment. Our courses are enjoyable, and our coaches will ensure your child has a great time!<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;How are your team of staff selected?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">We have an excellent team of staff hand picked to ensure your child has an unforgettable experience within our camps. We are proud to have a diverse range of coaches from a range of sporting backgrounds some achieving National and International status within their sport. <\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">We always have more applicants than positions so we are able to be very selective in our recruitment. All staff are fully trained and are cleared through the Disclosure and Barring Service (DBS) at an Enhanced Level. We also provide initial Safeguarding, Child Protection and First Aid courses for our team and follow up with refresher courses every 3 years.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;When do your camps run?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Our camps run through the school holidays, we offer Netball, Tennis, Multi-sports and an opportunity to do both in our Split day courses which compromise of Tennis in the morning and Multi- Sports in the afternoon.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Unfortunately we do not run on Bank Holidays.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;What are the timings?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">A full day on our Multi-Sports Camp Adventure Programme is 9am \u2013 4pm, half day is 9am \u2013 12.30pm and 1pm \u2013 4pm<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\">A full day on our Tennis\u00a0Camp is 9am \u2013 4pm, half day is 9am \u2013 12pm and 1pm \u2013 4pm<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">We also offer an Early drop off at 8am \u2013 9am and Late stay 4pm \u2013 5pm for both Tennis &amp; Multi-Sports camps.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\">Our Netball Camps offer a variety of different times and dates across numerous locations. <b>Please click the BOOK NOW button to see our different Netball camps.\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Arrival and collection&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">On arrival your child is signed in and settled in to their first activity, our Head coaches are available to discuss any immediate needs your child may have on the day not already noted within your booking. <\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Please allow time for arrival and collection as our team need to comply with necessary security procedures.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\">Please note \u2013 pick up from Multi-sports camp is not permitted before 3.45pm unless previously agreed with the camp manager.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;What if I\u2019m delayed?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Please notify us as soon as practically possible so we can let your child\/ren know. Don\u2019t worry, your child will be well cared for until your arrival. Payment for late collections or additional late stay requests can be made on the day.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\">There will be an additional charge applied for late collections, please see below;<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\">If more than 10 minutes late for a normal pick up a \u00a34 charge will be applied.<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\">If more than 10 minutes late for a late stay pick up (after 5pm) an \u00a310 charge will applied for every 30 minutes that you are late.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;What if my child is not well and cannot attend?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>If your child is unwell on the day of the camp unfortunately we cannot offer a refund. However, if you get in touch with us before 8.30am on the day of your camp\/course we will give you credit to use another time. There will be a \u00a35 admin charge to pay in order to do this.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Where are they located?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Our Multi-Sports camps run from Wodson Park and\/or Allenburys&#8217; GSK Sports Centre, Ware and Hitchin Girls School sports centre, Hitchin.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Our Tennis camp runs from HGS sports centre, Hitchin.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\">Our Netball Camps operate from a range of locations. <b>Please click the book now button to see what we have on offer.\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Who can participate in camps?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">For our Multi-Sports Camp Adventure Programme all children aged 5 on or before Sept 1st right up to and including 14 yrs of age can participate.\u00a0<\/span><span class=\"s1\">Children who will be still be aged 4 on or after Sept 1st are only permitted to attend for up to 4 hours.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\">Our Netball camps cater for children aged 8-14.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;My child may need extra assistance, is this something you can accommodate?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">We want to ensure every child gets to enjoy our uPlaySports activities. Please contact us in advance to discuss your individual needs. We can offer a 1-2-1 service at an additional cost or an adult friend can come along to offer assistance throughout the day. <\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">There may be some activities that may prove unsuitable, we can discuss this in advance. Please note we do not have the provisions to offer intimate care.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;How are the groups split? \u2013 (Multi-Sports Camp Adventure Programme only)&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p><span class=\"s1\">The groups are split on age. The younger group will normally be comprised of children up aged 8 and under and the older group ages 8-14. If your child would rather go in the older\/younger group we will always accommodate the request as long as we feel they are capable.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Which activities are included in Multi-Sports?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">A fun, action packed day of sports activities with a variety of activities such as Trampolining, Gymnastics, Badminton, Table Tennis, Kwik Cricket, Football, Basketball, Bench ball, Arts and Crafts, Games, Athletics, Uni-Hockey, Dodgeball, Parachute games, and more\u2026.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Should we need to withdraw any of the activities, for example as a result of unsuitable weather conditions or equipment failure, we will re-instate them as soon as is practically possible.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\">The daily activity plan is subject to change depending on space available and weather conditions.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;What happens if it rains?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">We love the Great British weather and we are prepared for everything! Some activities will be withdrawn in wet weather for safety reasons. <\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">We have an exciting range of activities using both indoor and outdoor facilities so whatever the weather your child will have an action packed day.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;What if my child has an accident?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p><span class=\"s1\">Accidents do happen, normally bumps and grazes as with any sporting activity. All our staff are first aid trained, any minor accident during camp will be treated, recorded and you will be notified on collection. In the unlikely event that a more serious injury occur we will of course contact you straight away.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;My child has medication that may \/ will need to be administered during the day, can this be accommodated?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p><span class=\"s1\">Please contact us in advance of making your booking to talk us through your child\u2019s individual needs.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;How do I book?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p><span class=\"s1\">All bookings are taken through our website. Please click the big red BOOK NOW button in the top right of the screen.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;I\u2019ve made an error with my booking, what should I do?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Don\u2019t panic! Our camps are very busy so please contact us straight away, we will do our very best to accommodate any day changes or timings.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\">Please note a \u00a35 administration fee will be applied to change your booking.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;What does my child need to bring?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">We provide all equipment needed for camp so your child does not need to bring anything other than a packed lunch, sports water bottle, additional clothing if needed and sun protection \/ Hat. <\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">We do not have refrigeration facilities on site, please use a small cool pack or frozen juice carton to keep contents cool until lunch.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">We have drinking water on site so all water bottles can be refilled throughout the day.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Do they need money?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p><span class=\"s1\">We have a tuck shop on our Multi-Sports Camp Adventure Programme where small treats can be purchased during lunch. Tuck Shop Prices: Sweets,\u00a010p \u2013 60p, Drinks, \u00a075p \u2013 \u00a31.30<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;What do they need to wear?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Recognised sports clothing and clean non-marking trainers must be worn, additional clothing if needed. Jeans, singlets and beach shorts are not appropriate. <\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">All clothing and belongings should be marked with your child\u2019s name.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\">Please note Netball and Tennis Clothing requirements may differ, please check out individual product guidelines for further information. Don\u2019t worry if you are unsure, please email office@uplaysports.co.uk and we will be happy to help.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;What shouldn\u2019t my child bring to camp?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.0.9&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">We strongly advise that children do not bring mobile phones or any electronic devices such as ipads, iPods etc. There is no real use for these items and they are often mislaid as children are busy with our daily programme of activities.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Staff are trained not to put themselves in a difficult position by taking care of such items and we cannot accept responsibility if they are lost or stolen. Our insurance does not cover such items.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Mobile phones: Although we understand the need for older children who make their way to and from camp to have a mobile phone, they are not allowed to be used once on camp, during break times or for photographs. They must be kept in personal baggage at the risk of the owner at all times. Please ensure your child is aware of this.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">Due to health and hygiene reasons, we are unfortunately unable to allow any birthday cakes (or any other food treats) to be brought onto our camps to be shared with the groups.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][\/et_pb_accordion][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Frequently Asked QuestionsHere at uPlayMultiSports we deliver high quality multi-sport coaching programmes for children. Our ethos is about participation, staying active and having fun! We want everyone who comes to our camps to enjoy experiencing as wide a range of activities as possible in a safe and friendly environment. Our courses are enjoyable, and our [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_et_pb_use_builder":"on","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":""},"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v14.9 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Frequently Asked Questions - uPlay Sports<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.uplaysports.co.uk\/faq\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Frequently Asked Questions - uPlay Sports\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.uplaysports.co.uk\/faq\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"uPlay Sports\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\" content=\"2020-01-27T19:48:07+00:00\" \/>\n<meta name=\"twit